body_html: Do you have a copy of protobuf installed by brew in /usr/local/include? If so, if you could unlink it and then build again, I think that will help. Otherwise, can you get us the full command line which was used to build the file that failed?

body: Do you have a copy of protobuf installed by brew in `/usr/local/include`? If so, if you could unlink it and then build again, I think that will help. Otherwise, can you get us the full command line which was used to build the file that failed?
